Welcome to ArchBang Live Iso

If you are reading this it is likely you do not have a working network connection.

Right click on network icon on panel [below right] and select 'Edit Connections'

If you want to use pacman package manager you need to edit mirrorlist

Open a terminal (Super+t or select from main menu)

sudo medit /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist

Remove unwanted mirrors, leaving only those nearest to your location

Then run

sudo pacman -Syyu

To install flash then use

sudo pacman -S flashplugin

Or a video player

sudo pacman -S gnome-mplayer







